undreds-of-complaints-over-sabrina-carpenter-and-charli-xcxs-2025-brit-awards-appearances-3843993">在家中以歌曲和分裂的歌迷</a>开幕。</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-cover-dexys-midnight-runners-come-on-eileen-in-london-3845546">观看Sabrina Carpenter封面Dexys Midnight Runners在伦敦的“ Come On on Eileen”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
