建筑师的山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）最初想要吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-sam-carter-originally-want--guitarist-guitarist--adam-christianson----- band-tollowlollowing-2024-transphobic-transphobic-conthopic-controversy-3845498?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = Architects-sam-carter-originally-werted-guitarist-adam-adam-adam-christianson-of band-the-band-the-the-the-the-the-the-the-the-2024-2024-transphobic-transphobic-controversySurej Singh Wed, 12 Mar 2025 02:56:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3845498 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我一团糟。我在想：“他必须走””</p><p>邮政建筑师的山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）最初是在2024年的跨性别争议之后首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-sam-carter-originally-wanted-guitarist-adam-christianson-out-of-the-band-following-2024-transphobic-controversy-3845498">的吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森（Adam Christianson）之后的乐队</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">建筑师的</a>主持人山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-speak-out-on-bands-political-views-after-controversial-post-shared-by-guitarist-adam-christianson-3576866">在去年年初，后者的跨性别和同性恋争议</a>之后，他最初希望吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森（Adam Christianson）退出乐队。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">新专辑《天空》，《地球与全部》中的建筑师”：“如果我们现在不打算发挥自己的潜力，我们什么时候？”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 2024年1月，克里斯蒂安森（Christianson）<a href="https://x.com/Timcast/status/1747757208308158719" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在政治评论员蒂姆·普尔（Tim Pool）最初在X（以前为Twitter）上重新发布了X（以前是Twitter）的视频</a><a href="https://twitter.com/SStricklandMMA/status/1747734279516250446" target="_blank" rel="noopener">后</a>，引起了粉丝和乐队成员的愤怒。</p><p>在有争议的视频中，斯特里克兰谈到了过去的一篇文章，他说：“如果我有一个同性恋儿子，我会认为我是一个人，无法成为一个造成如此弱点的人。” He also spoke about past anti-trans posts, adding: “10 years ago, to be trans was a mental fucking illness.现在，突然之间，像您这样的人在世界上他妈的weake之以鼻。你是一种感染。您是弱点的定义。 Everything that is wrong with the world is because of fucking you.”</p><p> Pool subsequently reposted the footage on X, calling Strickland a “fucking A+ guy” and hitting out at “the infection that is the woke left”. It was this message that Christianson reshared on his feed, but it has since been removed. </p><figure id="attachment_3828874" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828874" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828874" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="Architects frontman Sam Carter" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828874" class="wp-caption-text"> Architects frontman Sam Carter at Annexet on January 31, 2024 in Stockholm, Sweden CREDIT: Iwi Onodera/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> The musician later posted an apology, which read: “Shit!转发是一次完全事故！！ I don&#39;t endorse anything that guy says other than fuck Trudeau. Sorry for the panic everyone! Complete all-thumbs moment.”</p><p> However, despite the quick delete and apology, social media and fans at shows began turning on Christianson and the band as a whole. Speaking to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2025/feb/21/to-say-theres-no-future-is-counterproductive-metal-megastars-architects-on-grief-climate-and-hope-for-humanity" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Guardian</em></a> , frontman Sam Carter shared that upon first learning of the repost saga, he initially wanted the guitarist fired from the band.</p><p> “I was a mess.我在想：他必须走。 And then he wakes up and we have a phone conversation,” Carter explained. “He&#39;s my friend who picked me up off the floor when I was in bits crying about Tom; he&#39;s a stepdad of two kids; he&#39;s a saint. But you&#39;ve drawn this picture up of him. [The internet] is such a fucking scary place.”</p><p> Drummer Dan Searle chimed in, weighing in on social media&#39;s reaction: “They wanted Adam crucified in the street, with no job. Anything less than that would be an act of blatant transphobia.”</p><p> A couple of weeks later, Architects returned to the live stage and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-speak-out-on-bands-political-views-after-controversial-post-shared-by-guitarist-adam-christianson-3576866">clarified their stance on the homophobia and transphobia</a> . Addressing the Paris crowd, Carter said: “No one on this stage judges anybody for their gender, their race, and whoever they are in love with.我们从来没有。我们永远不会。 That is not what this band stands for, and it is not what this band will ever stand for. We love every single one of you.” </p><figure id="attachment_3426767" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3426767" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3426767" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns.jpg" alt="Sam Carter of Architects. Credit: Mariano Regidor via Redferns" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3426767" class="wp-caption-text"> Sam Carter of Architects. Credit: Mariano Regidor via Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> In other news, Architects have recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-announce-2025-uk-and-european-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3845013">announced a UK and European headline tour for 2025</a> . Brighton Metalcore乐队将于今年秋天在上个月发行的第11张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">《 Sky，The Earth＆Whoot Mooke》的第11张专辑“ The Sky，The Earth＆All Mooken”</a> （由前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Bring Me Horizo​​n</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jordan-fish">Jordan Fish</a>制作）。</p><p>门票将于本周五（3月14日）在GMT/GMT上午10点进行通用销售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Farchitects-tickets%2Fartist%2F1615917" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://www.architectsofficial.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（欧洲）购买您的门票。另外，粉丝本周可以通过<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Farchitects-tickets%2Fartist%2F1615917" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ticketmaster</a>访问各种预售。</p><h3><strong>建筑师的秋季2025年英国和欧洲巡演日期是：</strong></h3><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>01  -  Zenith  - 慕尼黑，de</strong><br /> <strong>03  - 保时捷竞技场，斯图加特，de<br /> 04  - 杜塞尔多夫（Duesseldorf）的三菱电气哈雷<br />05  -  Festhalle，Frankfurt，de<br /> 07  -  Ziggo Dome，Amsterdam，NL<br /> 08  - 巴克莱竞技场，汉堡，德<br />10  - 英国曼彻斯特的合作社直播<br />11  - 英国加的夫的Utilita Arena<br /> 12  -  O2，英国伦敦</strong></p><p>建筑师计划于今晚（3月10日）开始他们的2025年春季欧洲巡回演出。今年夏天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-2025-world-stadium-tour-wembley-buy-tickets-3812660">该小组将在他们的欧洲巡回演唱会的精选日期为林肯公园开放，</a>然后前往美国参加一场节日。</p><p>负责人山姆·卡特（Sam Carter） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">在去年年底在<em>NME</em>讲话时</a>解释说：“长大后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">林肯公园（Linkin Park）</a>对我和我的人声都有极大的影响力。如果您13岁那年告诉我，我将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>和Linkin Park一起参加体育场，我将永远不会 - 在我最疯狂的梦中 - 相信您。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="建筑师的山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）在皇家阿尔伯特·霍尔（Albert Hall）的直播中，与比菲·克莱罗（Biffy Clyro）和“ blegh！”合作。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tCcgOSlYrtI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当被问及有关建筑师2025年的现场计划时，鼓手丹·塞尔（Dan Searle）告诉<em>NME</em> ，英国巡回演唱会“肯定是逾期的”。他继续说：“我们与打英国有奇怪的关系，因为我们花了很多时间在国外旅行。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-sam-carter-originally-wanted-guitarist-adam-christianson-out-of-the-band-following-2024-transphobic-controversy-3845498">Architects&#39; Sam Carter originally wanted guitarist Adam Christianson out of the band following 2024 transphobic controversy</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
